About Einstein Discovery

Use Einstein Discovery to augment your data analysis by exposing relevant facts, themes, and statistical correlations in your data. It walks you through what has happened and why, what has changed, what is likely to happen, and what you can do about it.

Einstein Discovery stories are now models.
Explain and Predict Outcomes

A model helps you explore relationships between a business-relevant outcome and the possible factors that can potentially influence the outcome. For example, a model can focus on margin as the outcome variable and consider business data as potential contributing factors to the margin.

Configuration

Define the data and analytical settings that Einstein Discovery uses to generate insights and build predictive models. Settings include the outcome variable, whether to maximize or minimize the outcome variable, and other preferences.

Data Insights

Explore descriptive and diagnostic analysis Einstein Discovery provides to find answers and explanations about your data as they relate to the outcome you're interested in. Let Einstein Discovery highlight meaningful relationships in your data, then dive deeper to learn more.

Collaboration

Depending on your user permissions, you can create and share models with others.
